296
00:13:53,519 --> 00:13:56,159
You also had Lady Zhou poison the wife

297
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,720
of the Minister, forcing her to kill me.

298
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,200
Do you admit

299
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:01,120
to these things or not?

300
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,080
You...

301
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,080
You are foolish!

302
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,720
Why would you do such treacherous things?

303
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,840
You have trampled on the family's honor

304
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,519
and the court's laws!

305
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,559
My lord,

306
00:14:12,759 --> 00:14:15,039
how can you believe her alone?

307
00:14:16,679 --> 00:14:17,679
All these years,

308
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:20,360
I've managed the Xiao Family inside and out,

309
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,879
never once overstepping my bounds.

310
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,120
And I've always been

311
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:27,519
nothing but kind to Yunzhou

312
00:14:27,519 --> 00:14:28,720
and Madam Yin.

313
00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:31,159
How could I possibly do such a thing?

314
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:33,360
Nong,

315
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,000
bring that person up here.

316
00:14:38,679 --> 00:14:39,240
Let's go.

317
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:39,960
On your knees!

318
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,080
My lady,

319
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:46,279
do you recognize

320
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:47,399
this person?
